---
---

<section data-animate class="py-20 sm:py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background accents -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-[#f97316] opacity-[0.03] rounded-full blur-[100px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[300px] h-[300px] bg-[#3b82f6] opacity-[0.03] rounded-full blur-[80px] translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/3 pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Photo area with creative animation -->
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start">
        <div class="about-photo-wrap relative">
          <!-- Outer rotating gradient ring -->
          <div class="about-ring-outer absolute inset-[-16px] rounded-[32px] pointer-events-none"></div>
          <!-- Inner subtle ring -->
          <div class="about-ring-inner absolute inset-[-8px] rounded-[28px] border border-[#f97316]/20 pointer-events-none"></div>

          <!-- Photo container — swap the div below for <img src="/francisco.png" ...> when ready -->
          <div class="about-photo relative w-64 h-72 sm:w-72 sm:h-80 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-[#0f172a]/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e293b] flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Placeholder: replace with transparent-bg photo -->
            <!-- <img src="/francisco.png" alt="Francisco Sousa" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" /> -->
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl font-bold" style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #fb923c, #f59e0b); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">FS</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Subtle scanline overlay for depth -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-transparent to-[#0f172a]/30 pointer-events-none"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Availability badge -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-lg z-10">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#25d366] rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#0f172a]">Disponível</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating skill badge 1 -->
          <div class="about-badge-1 absolute -bottom-3 -left-4 bg-[#0f172a] text-white rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-xl z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold">Full-Stack</span>
          </div>

          <!-- Floating skill badge 2 -->
          <div class="about-badge-2 absolute top-6 -right-14 bg-[#f97316] text-white rounded-xl px-3 py-2 shadow-xl z-10 hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">Flutter · Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-[#f97316] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Sobre mim</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#0f172a] mb-6" style="font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;">
          Olá, eu sou o Francisco.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Cresci em Cascais, entre o oceano e o código. Sou <strong class="text-[#0f172a] font-semibold">Engenheiro Informático</strong> e, ao mesmo tempo, instrutor de skate — duas áreas que aparentemente não têm nada a ver, mas que me ensinaram que a persistência e a criatividade resolvem qualquer problema.
          </p>
          <p>
            Trabalho como freelancer, o que significa que quando fala comigo, está a falar com a <strong class="text-[#0f172a] font-semibold">pessoa que vai construir o seu projeto do início ao fim</strong> — sem intermediários, sem burocracia, sem surpresas. Websites, apps móveis, plataformas à medida: se tem um negócio e uma ideia, eu tenho a solução técnica.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value props -->
        <div class="mt-8 mb-8 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-[#f8fafc] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#f97316]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0f172a]">Só paga quando estiver satisfeito</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">50% para começar, 50% na entrega final aprovada</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-[#f8fafc] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#25d366]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#25d366" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.362 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.338 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0f172a]">Contacto direto por WhatsApp</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Sem formulários, sem esperas — fale diretamente comigo</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-[#f8fafc] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg bg-[#3b82f6]/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#0f172a]">30 dias de suporte grátis</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Após entrega, continuo disponível sem custo extra</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Rotating gradient ring around photo */
  .about-ring-outer {
    background: conic-gradient(
      from 0deg,
      transparent 0%,
      #f97316 20%,
      transparent 40%,
      transparent 60%,
      #f59e0b 80%,
      transparent 100%
    );
    opacity: 0.25;
    border-radius: 28px;
    animation: ring-rotate 6s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes ring-rotate {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  /* Floating badges animation */
  .about-badge-1 {
    animation: badge-float 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .about-badge-2 {
    animation: badge-float 4s ease-in-out 0.7s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes badge-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .about-ring-outer { animation: none !important; }
    .about-badge-1, .about-badge-2 { animation: none !important; }
  }
</style>
